其每年 50% 的增速。 此外，「殖民火星」一直是马斯克的目标，「我在想，八年之后会是什么样子呢？」马斯克感慨说，「如果幸运的话，也许我们会在八年内把人类送上火星。」 来源：澎湃新闻马斯克：SpaceX 每年保持 50% 发射增速，八年内送人类上火星"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "8 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/639667517"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2qSB/fWfltIDEAMaCTEwNDQyNjQxMiCegJWtBjAAOBtAHHIJNjM5NjY3NTE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1705372301.294581", "card_id": "Q_636103514", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 142}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "立「职场人设」突然走红，个体真的能把「工作人格」和「真实自我」长期分开？这是否是健康的应对？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-70c6c1f7031683f5d9e47aaf16a38493_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "7 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/636103514"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI2qSB/fWfltIDEAMaCTEwMzYzNDY5OSDdw5SsBjAAOIMCQB1yCTYzNjEwMzUxNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1705372301.296144", "card_id": "Q_639212230", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 86}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何在年终述职或报告中，做「恰到好处的自我批评」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-96688dabcbc9bd558833bcec7c868f24_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "7 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/639212230"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI2qSB/fWfltIDEAMaCTEwNDMyNTExNiCg9IOtBjAAOJ0EQB5yCTYzOTIxMjIzMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1705372301.301167", "card